  "pageTitle": "AI waste sorting machine for high-value plastic recycling",
  "bodyHtml": "<main class=\"product-page product-page-ai\">\n      <section class=\"section split-section\">\n        <div>\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">AI Optical Sorter for Waste</p>\n          <h1>AI waste sorting machine for high-value plastic recycling</h1>\n          <p class=\"hero-copy\">The WEI LAN AI optical sorter for waste identifies PET bottles, HDPE bottles, PP, and other mixed plastics by material and color. Modular configurations support automated waste sorting systems, MRF equipment upgrades, and compact smart recycling facilities that need stable continuous sorting.</p>\n          <div class=\"hero-actions\">\n            <a class=\"text-link is-hud\" href=\"/contact\">Request Proposal</a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"../assets/images/recyclable-plastic-sorting-line.webp\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <img src=\"/assets/images/recyclable-plastic-sorting-line.png\" alt=\"AI optical sorting line for recyclable plastic waste\">\n        </picture>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section\" id=\"models\" aria-labelledby=\"models-title\">\n        <div class=\"section-heading\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">Model parameters</p>\n          <h2 id=\"models-title\">GL01V series</h2>\n          <p>Three configurations on a shared AI sorting platform. Choose by throughput and material categories.</p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"spec-card-grid spec-card-grid-ai\">\n          <article class=\"spec-card spec-card-ai is-tier-1\">\n            <header class=\"spec-card-head\">\n              <span class=\"spec-card-rank\">SYS-01</span>\n              <div class=\"spec-card-id\">\n                <p class=\"spec-card-model\">GL01V1-5</p>\n                <p class=\"spec-card-tier\">Mini</p>\n              </div>\n              <span class=\"spec-card-status\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                <i></i><i></i>\n              </span>\n            </header>\n            <dl class=\"spec-metrics\">\n              <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:35%\">\n                <dt>Capacity</dt>\n                <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">0.6&ndash;0.8<small>t/h</small></span></dd>\n                <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:55%\">\n                <dt>Power</dt>\n                <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">30<small>kW</small></span></dd>\n                <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:38%\">\n                <dt>Footprint</dt>\n                <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">24<small>m<sup>2</sup></small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">installed footprint · 8 &times; 3 m layout · 3 m clear height</span></dd>\n                <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:50%\">\n                <dt>Sorting scope</dt>\n                <dd class=\"spec-scope\"><span class=\"spec-value\">5<small>material types</small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix spec-scope-summary\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-label=\"Full sorting scope: clear PET · color PET · HDPE · PP · mixed plastics\" data-scope-detail=\"clear PET · color PET · HDPE · PP · mixed plastics\">PET · HDPE · PP · Mixed</span></dd>\n                <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n              </div>\n            </dl>\n          </article>\n\n          <article class=\"spec-card spec-card-ai is-tier-2\">\n            <header class=\"spec-card-head\">\n              <span class=\"spec-card-rank\">SYS-02</span>\n              <div class=\"spec-card-id\">\n                <p class=\"spec-card-model\">GL01V2-9</p>\n                <p class=\"spec-card-tier\">Standard</p>\n              </div>\n              <span class=\"spec-card-status\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                <i></i><i></i>\n              </span>\n            </header>\n            <dl class=\"spec-metrics\">\n              <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:58%\">\n                <dt>Capacity</dt>\n                <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">0.8&ndash;1.2<small>t/h</small></span></dd>\n                <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:78%\">\n                <dt>Power</dt>\n                <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">45<small>kW</small></span></dd>\n                <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:62%\">\n                <dt>Footprint</dt>\n                <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">36<small>m<sup>2</sup></small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">installed footprint · 12 &times; 3 m layout · 6 m clear height</span></dd>\n                <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:90%\">\n                <dt>Sorting scope</dt>\n                <dd class=\"spec-scope\"><span class=\"spec-value\">9<small>material types</small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix spec-scope-summary\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-label=\"Full sorting scope: clear PET · green PET · blue PET · mixed-color PET · white HDPE · colored HDPE · PP · mixed plastics · reject\" data-scope-detail=\"clear PET · green PET · blue PET · mixed-color PET · white HDPE · colored HDPE · PP · mixed plastics · reject\">PET colors · HDPE · PP · Mixed · Reject</span></dd>\n                <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n              </div>\n            </dl>\n          </article>\n\n          <article class=\"spec-card spec-card-ai is-tier-3\">\n            <header class=\"spec-card-head\">\n              <span class=\"spec-card-rank\">SYS-03</span>\n              <div class=\"spec-card-id\">\n                <p class=\"spec-card-model\">GL01V3-10</p>\n                <p class=\"spec-card-tier\">Plus</p>\n              </div>\n              <span class=\"spec-card-status\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                <i></i><i></i>\n              </span>\n            </header>\n            <dl class=\"spec-metrics\">\n              <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:95%\">\n                <dt>Capacity</dt>\n                <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">1.5&ndash;2<small>t/h</small></span></dd>\n                <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:92%\">\n                <dt>Power</dt>\n                <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">53<small>kW</small></span></dd>\n                <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:92%\">\n                <dt>Footprint</dt>\n                <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">51<small>m<sup>2</sup></small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">installed footprint · 17 &times; 3 m layout · 6 m clear height</span></dd>\n                <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:100%\">\n                <dt>Sorting scope</dt>\n                <dd class=\"spec-scope\"><span class=\"spec-value\">10<small>material types</small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix spec-scope-summary\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-label=\"Full sorting scope: clear PET · green PET · blue PET · mixed-color PET · white HDPE · colored HDPE · PP · PE · mixed plastics · reject\" data-scope-detail=\"clear PET · green PET · blue PET · mixed-color PET · white HDPE · colored HDPE · PP · PE · mixed plastics · reject\">PET colors · HDPE · PP · PE · Mixed · Reject</span></dd>\n                <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n              </div>\n            </dl>\n          </article>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section sorting-performance-section\" aria-labelledby=\"sorting-performance-title\">\n        <div class=\"sorting-performance-head\">\n          <div>\n            <p class=\"eyebrow\">Sorting Performance</p>\n            <h2 id=\"sorting-performance-title\">AI sorting performance built around measurable recovery</h2>\n            <p>GL01V combines AI recognition, optical sensing, air-jet ejection, cyclic conveying, and digital reporting in a compact sorting center for plastic recycling and MRF upgrades.</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"sorting-feed-panel\" aria-labelledby=\"sorting-feed-title\">\n          <div>\n            <p class=\"sorting-panel-kicker\">Feed material</p>\n            <h3 id=\"sorting-feed-title\">Configured for bottle and rigid plastic recovery</h3>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"sorting-feed-grid\" aria-label=\"Recognized plastic stream examples\">\n            <span class=\"sorting-feed-chip chip-clear\"><b>PET</b><small>clear</small></span>\n            <span class=\"sorting-feed-chip chip-green\"><b>PET</b><small>green</small></span>\n            <span class=\"sorting-feed-chip chip-blue\"><b>PET</b><small>blue</small></span>\n            <span class=\"sorting-feed-chip chip-pet-mixed\"><b>PET</b><small>mixed-color</small></span>\n            <span class=\"sorting-feed-chip chip-hdpe\"><b>HDPE</b><small>white</small></span>\n            <span class=\"sorting-feed-chip chip-hdpe-colored\"><b>HDPE</b><small>colored</small></span>\n            <span class=\"sorting-feed-chip chip-pp\"><b>PP</b><small>rigid</small></span>\n            <span class=\"sorting-feed-chip chip-pe\"><b>PE</b><small>target</small></span>\n            <span class=\"sorting-feed-chip chip-mixed\"><b>Mixed</b><small>plastics</small></span>\n            <span class=\"sorting-feed-chip chip-reject\"><b>Reject</b><small>stream</small></span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"sorting-data-band\" aria-label=\"GL01V sorting performance metrics\">\n          <div class=\"sorting-data-copy\">\n            <p class=\"sorting-panel-kicker\">Compact sorting center</p>\n            <h3>High recovery data in a retrofit-ready footprint</h3>\n            <p>Mini, Standard, and Plus layouts scale from compact pilot lines to larger MRF sorting upgrades while keeping the same AI/HUD operating logic.</p>\n            <div class=\"sorting-mode-switch\" aria-label=\"Layout states\">\n              <span>Working</span>\n              <span>Transport</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"sorting-data-grid\">\n            <article>\n              <span>Categories</span>\n              <strong>10<small>types max</small></strong>\n            </article>\n            <article>\n              <span>Capacity</span>\n              <strong>2<small>t/h max</small></strong>\n            </article>\n            <article>\n              <span>Power</span>\n              <strong>30<small>kW min</small></strong>\n            </article>\n            <article>\n              <span>Footprint</span>\n              <strong>24<small>m<sup>2</sup> min</small></strong>\n            </article>\n            <article>\n              <span>Layout</span>\n              <strong>Skid<small>mounted</small></strong>\n            </article>\n            <article>\n              <span>Quick retrofit</span>\n              <strong>17<small>days fastest</small></strong>\n            </article>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"sorting-smart-panel\">\n          <div class=\"sorting-feature-intro\">\n            <p class=\"sorting-panel-kicker\">Smart machine</p>\n            <h3>Operator-ready control stack</h3>\n          </div>\n\n          <div class=\"sorting-feature-grid\" aria-label=\"Sorting center advantages\">\n            <article>\n              <span class=\"sorting-feature-icon icon-ai\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n              <h3>AI recognition</h3>\n              <p>Higher recovery value: AI identifies PET, HDPE, PP, PE, mixed plastics, and reject streams with less dependence on manual judgment.</p>\n            </article>\n            <article>\n              <span class=\"sorting-feature-icon icon-air\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n              <h3>Air-jet sorting</h3>\n              <p>Stable output purity: fast air-jet ejection removes targets accurately while the line keeps continuous throughput.</p>\n            </article>\n            <article>\n              <span class=\"sorting-feature-icon icon-sensors\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n              <h3>Sensor control</h3>\n              <p>Lower purity risk: live sensor signals expose recognition, pressure, timing, and material-flow drift before output quality drops.</p>\n            </article>\n            <article>\n              <span class=\"sorting-feature-icon icon-rate\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n              <h3>96-98% sorting rate</h3>\n              <p>96-98% sorting performance: brochure-listed accuracy supports high-purity recovery targets for plastic recycling and MRF upgrades.</p>\n            </article>\n            <article>\n              <span class=\"sorting-feature-icon icon-robot\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n              <h3>Robot-ready layout</h3>\n              <p>Lower labor pressure: robot-ready layout leaves room to reduce manual picking as material volume grows.</p>\n            </article>\n            <article>\n              <span class=\"sorting-feature-icon icon-cockpit\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n              <h3>Digital cockpit</h3>\n              <p>Faster decisions: live status, alarms, runtime, sorting statistics, carbon indicators, and video feeds are combined in one view.</p>\n            </article>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section dark-section product-process-section\" aria-labelledby=\"plastic-process-title\">\n        <div class=\"section-heading\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">Process Overview</p>\n          <h2 id=\"plastic-process-title\">Plastic recycling flow from feeding to digital reporting</h2>\n          <p>The optical sorting system is organized around a clear material path so buyers can evaluate where feeding, pre-sorting, material sorting, color sorting, and operating data fit into the production line.</p>\n        </div>\n        <ol class=\"process-timeline\" aria-label=\"Plastic recycling process\">\n          <li class=\"process-timeline-step\">\n            <span class=\"process-timeline-rank\">SYS-01</span>\n            <div class=\"process-timeline-card\">\n              <div class=\"process-timeline-body\">\n                <h3>Feeding</h3>\n                <p>Input post-consumer bottles or mixed recyclable plastics into the sorting line at a controlled rate.</p>\n              </div>\n              <figure class=\"process-timeline-media\" aria-label=\"Feeding process video\">\n                <div class=\"process-timeline-video\">\n                  <video controls playsinline preload=\"metadata\">\n                    <source src=\"/assets/video/AI上料.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                    Your browser does not support the video element.\n                  </video>\n                </div>\n              </figure>\n            </div>\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"process-timeline-step\">\n            <span class=\"process-timeline-rank\">SYS-02</span>\n            <div class=\"process-timeline-card\">\n              <div class=\"process-timeline-body\">\n                <h3>Pre-sorting</h3>\n                <p>Identify and separate metal containers from bottles made of other materials before downstream sorting.</p>\n              </div>\n              <figure class=\"process-timeline-media\" aria-label=\"Pre-sorting process video\">\n                <div class=\"process-timeline-video\">\n                  <video controls playsinline preload=\"metadata\">\n                    <source src=\"/assets/video/AI预分.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                    Your browser does not support the video element.\n                  </video>\n                </div>\n              </figure>\n            </div>\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"process-timeline-step\">\n            <span class=\"process-timeline-rank\">SYS-03</span>\n            <div class=\"process-timeline-card\">\n              <div class=\"process-timeline-body\">\n                <h3>Material sorting</h3>\n                <p>Separate plastics by target resin category to improve recovery value and reduce manual dependency.</p>\n              </div>\n              <figure class=\"process-timeline-media\" aria-label=\"Material sorting process video\">\n                <div class=\"process-timeline-video\">\n                  <video controls playsinline preload=\"metadata\">\n                    <source src=\"/assets/video/AI分拣.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                    Your browser does not support the video element.\n                  </video>\n                </div>\n              </figure>\n            </div>\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"process-timeline-step\">\n            <span class=\"process-timeline-rank\">SYS-04</span>\n            <div class=\"process-timeline-card\">\n              <div class=\"process-timeline-body\">\n                <h3>Color sorting</h3>\n                <p>Group PET bottles and other target materials by color where project value depends on cleaner fractions.</p>\n              </div>\n              <figure class=\"process-timeline-media\" aria-label=\"Color sorting process video\">\n                <div class=\"process-timeline-video\">\n                  <video controls playsinline preload=\"metadata\">\n                    <source src=\"/assets/video/AI出料.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                    Your browser does not support the video element.\n                  </video>\n                </div>\n              </figure>\n            </div>\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"process-timeline-step\">\n            <span class=\"process-timeline-rank\">SYS-05</span>\n            <div class=\"process-timeline-card\">\n              <div class=\"process-timeline-body\">\n                <h3>Digital reporting</h3>\n                <p>Track throughput, categories, equipment status, alerts, and carbon-related operating indicators.</p>\n              </div>\n              <figure class=\"process-timeline-media\" aria-label=\"Digital reporting video placeholder\">\n                <div class=\"process-timeline-video\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Video coming soon\">\n                  <span class=\"process-timeline-video-tag\">CAM-05</span>\n                  <span class=\"process-timeline-video-play\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n                  <span class=\"process-timeline-video-label\">Video coming soon</span>\n                </div>\n              </figure>\n            </div>\n          </li>\n        </ol>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section product-compare-section\" aria-labelledby=\"compare-title\" hidden>\n        <div class=\"section-heading\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">Product Comparison</p>\n          <h2 id=\"compare-title\">GL01V vs. industry baseline</h2>\n          <p>How the WEI LAN AI optical sorter stacks up against a typical sorting line on the metrics that drive total cost of ownership.</p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"product-compare-layout\">\n          <figure class=\"product-compare-explode\" aria-label=\"GL01V exploded view\">\n            <div class=\"product-compare-explode-frame\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Exploded view diagram coming soon\">\n              <span class=\"product-compare-explode-tag\">EXPLODED · GL01V2-9</span>\n              <span class=\"product-compare-explode-pin\" style=\"--pin-x:18%;--pin-y:32%\" data-label=\"01\"></span>\n              <span class=\"product-compare-explode-pin\" style=\"--pin-x:38%;--pin-y:58%\" data-label=\"02\"></span>\n              <span class=\"product-compare-explode-pin\" style=\"--pin-x:58%;--pin-y:26%\" data-label=\"03\"></span>\n              <span class=\"product-compare-explode-pin\" style=\"--pin-x:74%;--pin-y:64%\" data-label=\"04\"></span>\n              <span class=\"product-compare-explode-pin\" style=\"--pin-x:88%;--pin-y:40%\" data-label=\"05\"></span>\n              <span class=\"product-compare-explode-label\">Exploded view coming soon</span>\n            </div>\n            <figcaption>\n              <span class=\"product-compare-explode-meta\">5 modular skids · standard tooling</span>\n            </figcaption>\n          </figure>\n\n          <div class=\"product-compare-panel\">\n            <header class=\"product-compare-panel-head\">\n              <span class=\"product-compare-legend\">\n                <span class=\"product-compare-legend-mark is-self\"></span>WEI LAN GL01V\n              </span>\n              <span class=\"product-compare-legend\">\n                <span class=\"product-compare-legend-mark is-base\"></span>Industry baseline\n              </span>\n            </header>\n\n            <ul class=\"product-compare-list\" role=\"list\">\n              <li class=\"product-compare-row\" data-better=\"true\">\n                <div class=\"product-compare-row-head\">\n                  <span class=\"product-compare-row-id\">M-01</span>\n                  <h3>Part-to-whole ratio</h3>\n                  <span class=\"product-compare-row-unit\">% of unit cost</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-compare-bars\">\n                  <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-self\" style=\"--fill:38%\">\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">WEI LAN</span>\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">38%</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-base\" style=\"--fill:62%\">\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">Baseline</span>\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">62%</span>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <p class=\"product-compare-row-note\">Lower spare-part ratio means slower depreciation and lower lifetime maintenance cost.</p>\n              </li>\n\n              <li class=\"product-compare-row\" data-better=\"true\">\n                <div class=\"product-compare-row-head\">\n                  <span class=\"product-compare-row-id\">M-02</span>\n                  <h3>Footprint</h3>\n                  <span class=\"product-compare-row-unit\">m² for Standard tier</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-compare-bars\">\n                  <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-self\" style=\"--fill:55%\">\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">WEI LAN</span>\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">36 m²</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-base\" style=\"--fill:100%\">\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">Baseline</span>\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">65 m²</span>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <p class=\"product-compare-row-note\">Skid-mounted layout fits compact MRF rooms and roadside recycling stations.</p>\n              </li>\n\n              <li class=\"product-compare-row\" data-better=\"true\">\n                <div class=\"product-compare-row-head\">\n                  <span class=\"product-compare-row-id\">M-03</span>\n                  <h3>Capacity</h3>\n                  <span class=\"product-compare-row-unit\">t/h, Standard tier</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-compare-bars\">\n                  <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-self\" style=\"--fill:88%\">\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">WEI LAN</span>\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">0.8 – 1.2</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-base\" style=\"--fill:62%\">\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">Baseline</span>\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">0.6 – 0.9</span>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <p class=\"product-compare-row-note\">Optimised feed + AI recognition lifts throughput at the same footprint class.</p>\n              </li>\n\n              <li class=\"product-compare-row\" data-better=\"true\">\n                <div class=\"product-compare-row-head\">\n                  <span class=\"product-compare-row-id\">M-04</span>\n                  <h3>Power draw</h3>\n                  <span class=\"product-compare-row-unit\">kW, Standard tier</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-compare-bars\">\n                  <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-self\" style=\"--fill:60%\">\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">WEI LAN</span>\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">45 kW</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-base\" style=\"--fill:100%\">\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">Baseline</span>\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">75 kW</span>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <p class=\"product-compare-row-note\">Roughly 40% lower power per tonne sorted, calculated at rated throughput.</p>\n              </li>\n\n              <li class=\"product-compare-row\" data-better=\"true\">\n                <div class=\"product-compare-row-head\">\n                  <span class=\"product-compare-row-id\">M-05</span>\n                  <h3>Transport &amp; assembly</h3>\n                  <span class=\"product-compare-row-unit\">days to commission</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-compare-bars\">\n                  <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-self\" style=\"--fill:35%\">\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">WEI LAN</span>\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">3 – 5 days</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-base\" style=\"--fill:90%\">\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">Baseline</span>\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">10 – 14 days</span>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <p class=\"product-compare-row-note\">Pre-wired skid modules ship in standard containers; on-site work is bolt-and-cable only.</p>\n              </li>\n            </ul>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section ai-faq-section\" aria-labelledby=\"ai-faq-title\">\n        <div class=\"section-heading\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">FAQ</p>\n          <h2 id=\"ai-faq-title\">AI optical sorting questions buyers ask before RFQ</h2>\n          <p>These answers help recycling operators, EPC teams, and equipment buyers evaluate whether the AI optical sorter fits their material stream and project stage.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ai-faq-panel\">\n          <article class=\"ai-faq-item\">\n            <h3 class=\"ai-faq-question\"><span>Q-01</span>What materials can the AI optical sorter separate?</h3>\n            <p class=\"ai-faq-answer\">The system is designed for recyclable plastic streams such as PET bottles, HDPE bottles, PP, mixed rigid plastics, and color-based PET fractions including transparent, green, blue, and mixed-color bottles.</p>\n            <div class=\"faq-input-list\">\n              <span class=\"faq-input-label\">Required inputs</span>\n              <span>Material photos or videos</span>\n              <span>Target output categories</span>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"ai-faq-item\">\n            <h3 class=\"ai-faq-question\"><span>Q-02</span>What affects AI waste sorting machine price?</h3>\n            <p class=\"ai-faq-answer\">Price depends on throughput, material categories, number of sorting modules, feeding and baling scope, digital control requirements, installation support, and whether the project needs integration with existing MRF equipment.</p>\n            <div class=\"faq-input-list\">\n              <span class=\"faq-input-label\">Required inputs</span>\n              <span>Target throughput</span>\n              <span>Sorting module scope</span>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"ai-faq-item\">\n            <h3 class=\"ai-faq-question\"><span>Q-03</span>How much capacity can one optical sorting line handle?</h3>\n            <p class=\"ai-faq-answer\">The GL01V model range covers 0.6-2 t/h. Final sizing should be checked against material composition, contamination level, desired purity, available footprint, and daily operating hours.</p>\n            <div class=\"faq-input-list\">\n              <span class=\"faq-input-label\">Required inputs</span>\n              <span>Daily operating hours</span>\n              <span>Available footprint</span>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"ai-faq-item\">\n            <h3 class=\"ai-faq-question\"><span>Q-04</span>Can the system be added to an existing recycling facility?</h3>\n            <p class=\"ai-faq-answer\">Integration can be evaluated when the buyer provides the current process layout, feed condition, conveyor height, control requirements, and target output. The skid-mounted structure supports practical retrofit discussions.</p>\n            <div class=\"faq-input-list\">\n              <span class=\"faq-input-label\">Required inputs</span>\n              <span>Existing line layout</span>\n              <span>Conveyor height and control points</span>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section ai-rfq-section\" aria-labelledby=\"ai-rfq-title\">\n        <div class=\"section-heading\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">RFQ preparation</p>\n          <h2 id=\"ai-rfq-title\">Prepare the data package for AI sorter sizing</h2>\n          <p>Send these inputs before quotation so the engineering team can confirm sorting scope, equipment model, layout feasibility, and integration risks.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ai-rfq-checklist\">\n          <article>\n            <span>01</span>\n            <h3>Material photos or videos</h3>\n            <p>Show the feed stream on belt, bale condition, contamination level, and color mix in normal operating conditions.</p>\n          </article>\n          <article>\n            <span>02</span>\n            <h3>Target throughput</h3>\n            <p>Confirm hourly capacity, daily operating hours, peak load, and whether the line needs one or multiple sorting modules.</p>\n          </article>\n          <article>\n            <span>03</span>\n            <h3>Output categories</h3>\n            <p>List required fractions such as PET clear, PET green, PET blue, HDPE, PP, mixed plastic, or reject stream.</p>\n          </article>\n          <article>\n            <span>04</span>\n            <h3>Existing line layout</h3>\n            <p>Provide conveyor height, available footprint, upstream feeding method, downstream baler position, and control interface needs.</p>\n          </article>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"rfq-action-strip\">\n          <a class=\"primary-button\" href=\"/contact\">Request Engineering Review</a>\n          <a class=\"secondary-button\" href=\"/resources\">Prepare File Pack</a>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n    </main>"
}
